Package: submitr
Type: Package
Title: Handles submissions to a database of events in learnr sessions.
Version: 0.2.2
Author: Daniel Kaplan
Maintainer: Daniel Kaplan <kaplan@macalester.edu>
Description: The learnr tutorial system provides a hook by which user events can be logged. Submitr provides ways to connect to this hook so that events can be logged centrally, for instance to a Google Sheet.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: learnr,
         googledrive,
         googlesheets4 (>= 0.2.0),
         jsonlite,
         shiny,
         knitr
Remotes: tidyverse/googlesheets4
Extends: learnr
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests: 
    rmarkdown
